OL,3,CBudget 2024: What does it mean for
OL,4,CWales?
OL,6,FThe finance minister, who is the MS
OL,7,Ffor Gower, also said: "Yet again our
OL,8,Fcall for an Essentials Guarantee to
OL,9,Fensure that people on Universal Credit
OL,10,Fcan meet their essential costs was not
OL,11,Fheeded by the Chancellor. Instead, he
OL,12,Fhas chosen to cut employee National
OL,13,FInsurance Contributions by 2p."
OL,15,F"Apart from a few small announcements,
OL,16,Fthere was nothing in this Budget for
OL,17,FWales. Our core priorities for UK
OL,18,FGovernment investment in coal tip
OL,19,Fsafety and re-classification of HS2
OL,20,Fhave, once again, been ignored," she
OL,21,Fadded.
